      "title": "PM2.5",
      "description": "**Recommended level:** below 15 µg/m³ (24h average, WHO guideline).\n\n**What it affects:** fine particles penetrate deep into the lungs and bloodstream; they affect the respiratory and cardiovascular systems.\n\n**How to fix it:** close the windows if the source is outside, use a purifier with a HEPA filter, avoid smoking/burning indoors.",
